.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fB\-L\fR, \fB\-\-bandwidth\-limit\fR
.
.IP
Keep bandwidth usage under the specified (numeric) KBs
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-verbose\fR
.
.IP
Detailed output
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fB\-d\fR, \fB\-\-debug\fR
.
.IP
Enable full debug information and backtraces
.
.IP "\(bu" 4
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
.
.IP
